PN,31201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775639132
OL,3,CFirst ever photograph of the far-side
OL,4,Cof the moon released
OL,6,FHumans have seen the far-side of the
OL,7,Fmoon with the unaided eye for the
OL,8,Ffirst time, as the Artemis II crew
OL,9,Fpassed behind it during their lunar
OL,10,Fflyby.
OL,12,FThe White House released the first
OL,13,Fphoto taken by the crew of the far-
OL,14,Fside on Tuesday.
OL,16,F"Humanity, from the other side. First
OL,17,Fphoto from the far side of the Moon.
OL,18,FCaptured from Orion as Earth dips
OL,19,Fbeyond the lunar horizon," the
OL,20,Fpicture, dated April 6, was captioned
OL,21,Fon a post on X.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
