FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775639132
OL,3,CFirst ever photograph of the far-side
OL,4,Cof the moon released
OL,6,FThe White House shared the photograph
OL,7,Fin a second post to X, writing:
OL,8,F"Totality, beyond Earth. From lunar
OL,9,Forbit, the Moon eclipses the Sun,
OL,10,Frevealing a view few in human history
OL,11,Fhave ever witnessed".
OL,13,FThe Artemis II crew is made up of four
OL,14,FAmerican astronauts (Reid Wiseman,
OL,15,FVictor Glover, pilot and Christina
OL,16,FKoch) and one Canadian, Jeremy Hansen.
OL,18,FHansen described how the crew had been
OL,19,F"giddy" as they came within 4,067
OL,20,Fmiles (6,545km) of the moon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
