PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775639132
OL,3,CFirst ever photograph of the far-side
OL,4,Cof the moon released
OL,6,F"When we were on the far-side of the
OL,7,Fmoon and out of contact with planet
OL,8,FEarth, we all knew it. It was a
OL,9,Fmilestone, we saw Earth disappear, but
OL,10,Fwe were so busy with the science,"
OL,11,FHansen said.
OL,13,FThe spaceship launched from Kennedy
OL,14,FSpace Center in Florida on April 1.
OL,16,FIt will take the crew four days to get
OL,17,Fback to Earth, with a splashdown in
OL,18,Fthe Pacific expected on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
