PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775639132
OL,3,CFirst ever photograph of the far-side
OL,4,Cof the moon released
OL,6,FArtemis II is the second mission as
OL,7,Fpart of Nasa's lunar exploration
OL,8,Fprogramme Artemis, during which the
OL,9,Fspace agency are sending astronauts on
OL,10,F"increasingly difficult missions".
OL,12,F"We're going back to the Moon for
OL,13,Fscientific discovery, economic
OL,14,Fbenefits, and inspiration for a new
OL,15,Fgeneration of explorers", they say, as
OL,16,Fwell as to build on their foundation
OL,17,Ffor the "first crewed missions to
OL,18,FMars."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
