PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775639132
OL,3,CFirst ever photograph of the far-side
OL,4,Cof the moon released
OL,6,FArtemis is part of Nasa's longer-term
OL,7,Fplans to eventually build a lunar base
OL,8,Fon the surface of the moon, which
OL,9,Fwould allow astronauts to live and
OL,10,Fwork there.
OL,12,FWith the support of such a base, the
OL,13,Fspace agency would then be able to
OL,14,Fwork on the technology required to
OL,15,Fprotect a future Mars crew from lack
OL,16,Fof air, space radiation and extreme
OL,17,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
